FYI: I was able to fix this by changing the code for DataGrid.OnCanExecuteCancelEdit to this:

        protected virtual void OnCanExecuteCancelEdit(CanExecuteRoutedEventArgs e)
        {
            e.CanExecute = CanEndEdit(e, /* commit = */ false);
            if (e.CanExecute)
            {
                e.Handled = true;    
            }
            else
            {
                e.ContinueRouting = true;
            }
            
        }

That way, the escape key events will bubble up to the containing window.
